    {
      "id": "0e8095a3_0b9155a2",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/sdc/components/sdc-helm-validator/values.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 54,
      "message": "I'm not a java specialist but will our resources definitions work fine with the static java resource params that you have in your cmd line:\n[\"java\",\"-XX:+UseParallelGC\",\"-XX:MinRAMPercentage=50\",\"-XX:MaxRAMPercentage=50\",\"-XX:MinHeapFreeRatio=10\",\"-XX:MaxHeapFreeRatio=20\",\"-jar\",\"./opt/helmvalidator/helmvalidator.jar\"]",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 4965,
        "name": "Krzysztof Opasiak",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "k.opasiak@samsung.com",
        "username": "kopasiak"
      },
      "updated": "2021-04-15 10:08:43.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "4a23f9b2_fd7109df",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/sdc/components/sdc-helm-validator/values.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 54,
      "message": "Explanation: This entry point is for Java memory optimization. Since Java 11, JVM has possibility to calculate amount of HEAP memory based on available container resources. Default settings:\n1/2 memory -> when container has small limits (less than 256 mb) \n1/4 memory -> when container has large limits (more than 256) \n\nIf you set limits to 256 and 512 your heap still has 128 mb size. \n\nCurrent settings (XX:MinRAMPercentage=50, XX:MaxRAMPercentage=50\" )is not static, it is percentage of limits: 1/2 memory -> for any resource limits. \nMemory limit 256 -> heap size 128 \nMemory limit 512 -> heap size 256 .\nWe get linear memory calculation. \n--------\nXX:MinHeapFreeRatio=10 XX:MaxHeapFreeRatio=20 - it force garbage collector to release memory earlier - it is also percentage values. \n\nSource: \nhttps://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/gctuning/factors-affecting-garbage-collection-performance.html#GUID-5508674B-F32D-4B02-9002-D0D8C7CDDC75",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6310,
        "name": "Tomasz Wr�bel",
        "display_name": "Tomasz Wrobel",
        "email": "tomasz.wrobel@nokia.com",
        "username": "twrobel"
      },
      "updated": "2021-04-15 11:30:45.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "0e8095a3_0b9155a2",
      "unresolved": true
    },
